videoSnippet.description:

Have a great day :)

Roebers, Eline (2361) - L'Ami, Erwin (2627)
Tata Steel Challengers (chess24.com) [2] 2023.01.15
C95 Ruy Lopez, closed, Breyer, Borisenko variation

1.e4 e5 2.Nf3 Nc6 3.Bb5 a6 4.Ba4 Nf6 5.O-O Be7 6.Re1 b5 7.Bb3 d6 8.c3 O-O 9.h3 Nb8 10.d4 Nbd7 11.Nbd2 c5 12.Nf1 Re8 13.Ng3 Bf8 14.Bc2 Qc7 15.Be3 Bb7 16.d5 c4 17.Nh2 a5 18.Nf5 a4 19.a3 Kh8 20.g4 Nc5 21.Qf3 Ng8 22.g5 g6 23.Ng3 Be7 24.h4 Rf8 25.h5 Bc8 26.Qh1 Qd7 27.f4 Qh3 28.Qf3 exf4 29.Bd4+ f6 30.Qxf4 Nd7 31.Re3 Ne5 32.Nf5 Qxh5 33.Nxe7 Nxe7 34.gxf6 g5 35.Bxe5 gxf4 36.fxe7+ Kg8 37.exf8=Q+ Kxf8 38.Bxd6+ Ke8 39.Bxf4 Ra7 40.Kh1 Rg7 41.Rg1 Rxg1+ 42.Kxg1 Bg4 43.e5 Bf5 44.Bxf5 Qxf5 45.Bg3 Qb1+ 46.Nf1

06:40 Pause the Video!
09:00 It was in this position!
10:25 Contributions!

The 2023 Tata Steel Challengers is taking place from 14-29 January in Wijk aan Zee, the Netherlands. The 14-player single round-robin offers the winner an automatic place in the 2024 Tata Steel Masters.

The time control is 100 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 50 minutes for 20 moves, then 15 minutes for the rest of the game, with a 30-second increment per move from move 1. A tie for first place will be decided by two blitz (3+2) games. If still tied, the players keep playing single "sudden death" games where White gets 2.5 minutes and Black 3 minutes until one side wins. Official website: www.tatasteelchess.com
